## 1. INTRODUCTION
Welcome to your custom Termux development environment. 
This script is designed to centralize your GitHub 
projects, automations, and technical notes under 
a unique Retro-Pixel interface.

## 2. SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS
To ensure all features work at 100% capacity:
* [gh-cli]: GitHub CLI for authentication.
* [git]: Version control management.
* [bash]: Command-line interpreter.

## 3. PROJECT MANAGEMENT (GALLERY)
When entering the Gallery (Option 1#):
- You can view your latest 20 repositories.
- The (+) icon allows for instant public 
  repository creation.
- Ensure your personal TOKEN is configured via 
  'gh auth login' before use.

## 4. AUTOMATIONS (BUTTONS)
Any .sh script stored in the 'automations/' 
folder will automatically appear in menu 2#.

## 5. KEYBOARD SHORTCUTS
- [q] : Used to Go Back or Exit.
- [ENTER] : Confirm action or enter a menu.
- [UP/DOWN] : Navigate through options.

